extendedInfo.description: CAR ROAD TRIP PLANNER CHECKLISTIf you are planning your next Road Trip Vacation then you know how stressful it can be, trying to remember every single item that you will be needing for the trip.  Why not alleviate some of that stress with this handy checklist app.  Take a look below at everything you will have access to:- Comes pre-populated with over 130 items- Add/Delete Lists- Duplicate Old Lists so you don't have to start over- Add New Tasks- Add New Items- Delete Unwanted Items- Set Alarms to remind yourself of items you still need to do- Add Notes for more clarification- Set a Priority to items (High, Medium, Low)- Edit the Names of Items- Sort Your Lists Alphabetically or by Priority (Menu Item)kw: summer, spring, vacation, dad, mom, memories, fun, kids, children, boy, girl, baby, toddler, car, van, rv, to do, list, check
